# Welcome to MyKMS

This is your first note. You can:

- Create new notes using the + button
- Create folders using the folder+ button
- Link to other notes using [[note name]] syntax
- Click on links to navigate between notes
- Use the search bar to find notes
- Delete notes using the trash icon
- Drag and drop notes into folders

Try creating a new note and linking to it from here!
